sequenceDiagram
    participant MLApp as ML Application
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Online as Online Feature Store<br/>80/443 HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Redis as Redis<br/>6379/TCP TLS1.2+ (optional)
    participant Registry as Registry Server<br/>80/443 HTTP/gRPC

    Note over MLApp,Registry: Flow 1: Online Feature Retrieval (Real-time Inference)

    MLApp->>Route: POST /get-online-features<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: None/OIDC Bearer Token
    Route->>Online: Forward request<br/>HTTP/80 or HTTPS/443<br/>TLS1.2+ (optional)
    Online->>Registry: Query feature metadata<br/>HTTP/gRPC<br/>TLS1.2+ (optional)
    Registry-->>Online: Feature schema & config
    Online->>Redis: Retrieve pre-computed features<br/>Redis Protocol/6379<br/>Password auth (optional)
    Redis-->>Online: Feature values
    Online-->>Route: JSON response with features
    Route-->>MLApp: HTTPS response

    Note over MLApp,Registry: ---

    participant TrainingJob as Training Job
    participant Offline as Offline Feature Store<br/>80/443 HTTP/HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3/GCS Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over TrainingJob,S3: Flow 2: Historical Feature Retrieval (Model Training)

    TrainingJob->>Offline: POST /get-historical-features<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: None/OIDC/RBAC
    Offline->>Registry: Query feature definitions<br/>HTTP/gRPC<br/>TLS1.2+ (optional)
    Registry-->>Offline: Feature metadata
    Offline->>S3: Read Parquet files<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>AWS IAM/Service Account
    S3-->>Offline: Historical feature data
    Offline-->>TrainingJob: Processed features (DataFrame)

    Note over TrainingJob,S3: ---

    participant CronJob as CronJob Pod
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS1.2+ (optional)

    Note over CronJob,PG: Flow 3: Feature Materialization (Scheduled)

    CronJob->>Offline: Fetch latest feature values<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Service Account Token
    Offline->>S3: Read source data<br/>HTTPS/443
    S3-->>Offline: Raw feature data
    Offline-->>CronJob: Computed features
    CronJob->>Online: Write materialized features<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    Online->>Redis: Persist to online store<br/>Redis Protocol/6379
    Redis-->>Online: ACK
    Online-->>CronJob: Success

    Note over CronJob,PG: ---

    participant Operator as Feast Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over Operator,Prom: Flow 4: Operator Reconciliation

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch FeatureStore CR<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Service Account Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: CR change event
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Deployment<br/>HTTPS/6443
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: ACK
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Service<br/>HTTPS/6443
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: ACK
    Prom->>Operator: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    Operator-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics
